      </div>
      <div class="section-content reveal" style="margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center;">
        <p>Full service details on our <a href="/services/ai-search-optimisation/" class="inline-link">AI Search Optimisation</a> page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== FAQ ========== -->
  <section class="section faq-section" id="faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions about tuition centre AI search optimisation in Singapore">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
        <h2>Tuition Centre AI Search Optimisation — Questions Answered</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d1">
          <summary>Why does my tuition centre need AI search optimisation?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>Parents in Singapore increasingly ask ChatGPT and Gemini for tuition centre recommendations before enrolling their children. These are extremely high-intent queries — a parent asking AI for the best PSLE maths tutor is ready to act. If your centre isn't in the AI answer, you lose that enrolment.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d2">
          <summary>Which AI platforms do parents use to find tuition centres?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>The main platforms are ChatGPT, Google Gemini, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, and Microsoft Copilot. Parents also encounter AI-generated recommendations through Google's SGE results when searching for tuition-related queries.</p></div>
